{"word":"H4616 - מַעַן - maʻan - mah'-an - Because of","slug":"H4616","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מַעַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>maʻan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mah'-an"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Because of"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05E2;&#x05DF; - ma&#x201B;an</b> - <i>mah'-an</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6030\">H6030</a>; properly <i>heed</i>, that is, <i>purpose</i>; used only adverbially, <i>on account of</i> (as a motive or an aim), teleologically <i>in order that: - </i>because of, to the end (intent) that, for (to, . . . &lsquo;s sake), + lest, that, to."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3282\">H3282</a>, <a href=\"#/H4617\">H4617</a>, <a href=\"#/H5772\">H5772</a>, <a href=\"#/H6030\">H6030</a>, <a href=\"#/H6256\">H6256</a>, <a href=\"#/H6258\">H6258</a>, <a href=\"#/H6261\">H6261</a>, <a href=\"#/H6262\">H6262</a>, <a href=\"#/H6278\">H6278</a>"}]}